<objective>
Redesign the existing landing page at `/` into a conversion-focused marketing page with enhanced hero section, social proof, improved feature showcase, SEO meta tags, and full Polish/English localization.

Purpose: The current landing page (built in Phase 33) is functional but basic. This upgrade adds social proof, better visual design, dual CTAs, and SEO optimization to maximize sign-up conversion from first-time visitors.

Output: Enhanced `landing.html` with social proof section, OG/Twitter meta tags, improved hero with dual CTAs, full i18n coverage, and test coverage for all new sections.
</objective>

