  <action>
Redesign `app/templates/landing.html` with the following enhancements. Preserve the existing Jinja2 + Tailwind + i18n `t()` pattern used throughout.

**1. OG & Twitter meta tags (in `<head>`):**
Add after the existing `<meta name="description">`:
```html
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ t('landing.hero_title') }} — {{ t('app.name') }}">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ t('landing.meta_desc') }}">
<meta property="og:type" content="website">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ request.url }}">
<meta property="og:image" content="{{ request.base_url }}static/icons/icon-512.png">
<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
<meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ t('landing.hero_title') }} — {{ t('app.name') }}">
<meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ t('landing.meta_desc') }}">
```

**2. Enhanced nav bar:**
Keep the existing sticky nav. Add a "Register" / sign-up link next to the existing "Sign in" button:
- "Sign in" link: `href="/auth/login"` — text style (no background), uses `t('landing.nav_sign_in')`
- "Get Started" button: `href="/auth/login"` — filled indigo button, uses `t('landing.nav_get_started')`. Both go to /auth/login since Google OAuth handles new + existing.

**3. Enhanced hero section:**
- Keep the h1 with `t('landing.hero_title')` and subtitle `t('landing.hero_subtitle')`
- Replace the single CTA with TWO buttons:
  - Primary: "Start for free" → `/auth/login`, filled indigo-600 button with `shadow-lg shadow-indigo-500/25`
  - Secondary: "Sign in" → `/auth/login`, ghost/outline button with `border border-white/20`
- Below the CTAs add a trust line: `t('landing.trust_line')` — e.g. "No credit card required · Free forever for basic use"
- Keep the CSS-only calendar mockup but improve with subtle pulse animation on the highlighted day cells

**4. Social proof section (NEW — add between hero and features):**
Add a new section with id="social-proof":
```html
<section id="social-proof" class="py-16 border-y border-white/5">
```

Contents:
- Section title: `t('landing.social_proof_title')` — "Trusted by couples & families"
- 3 testimonial cards in a grid (md:grid-cols-3), each containing:
  - Quote text: `t('landing.testimonial_1')`, `t('landing.testimonial_2')`, `t('landing.testimonial_3')`
  - Author name: `t('landing.testimonial_1_author')`, etc.
  - Star rating: 5 gold stars using ★ character
- Below testimonials, a row of 3 trust badges:
  - "🔒 " + `t('landing.trust_privacy')` — "Your data stays private"
  - "⚡ " + `t('landing.trust_fast')` — "Lightning fast sync"
  - "🌍 " + `t('landing.trust_open')` — "Open source core"

Card styling: `rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-6` with `background: rgba(26,20,68,0.4)` (matching existing card style).

**5. Enhanced features section:**
Keep the existing 6-feature grid. Replace emoji icons with inline SVG icons for a more polished look. Keep the same i18n keys. Add `animate-in` classes with staggered delays for scroll reveal.

